 the Jewish past.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 31. Jan 2022) 0aHistoriographyzEuropexHistoryy20th century. 0aHolocaust, Jewish (1939-1945)xHistoriography. 0aJewish historians. 0aJewszEuropexHistoriography. 4aHistory -- Intellectual and Cultural. 4aHistory -- Jewish. 7aHISTORY / Jewish.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9780804773461zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780804773461423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780804773461/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles